<!--<h4><hi rend="italic">First Face.</hi></h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśubhajāta
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ka śakavarṣaṁbulu 1191
<lb n="3"/>yagunēṁṭi śu<unclear>kla</unclear>saṁvatsara kā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rttika śuddha paṁccamiyu gu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ruvāramunāṁḍu svasti sa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>mastabhuvanajanavikhyā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ta paṁcāśatavīraśāsa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>nalabdhānēkaguṇagaṇālaṁkri
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ta satyaśau<unclear>cācāracā</unclear>
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ritra nayavinayavipulavi
<lb n="11" break="no"/>jñāna vīrabalaṁjyadhaṁ
<lb n="12" break="no"/>rmapratipālitu
<lb n="13" break="no"/>laina pākanāṁḍiruvaiyo
<lb n="14" break="no"/>kkavēyiṁṭṭikini veṁggima
<lb n="15" break="no"/>dāṟuvēlakū nanmakoṁḍḍa
<lb n="16" break="no"/>vaṭṭaṇasthalaṁbunakuṁ bra
<lb n="17" break="no"/>bhumukhyulaina śrīma
<lb n="18" break="no"/>tu Ena<supplied reason="omitted">ma</supplied>ṁdalasthalamu pekka
<lb n="19" break="no"/>ṁḍḍru śrīmatugauṇīśva
<lb n="20" break="no"/>radēvamahāliṁggamu
</p>

<!--<h4><hi rend="italic">Second Face.</hi><note n="304-1">The figures of the crescent and the sun are engraved on the top.</note></h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="21"/>Aṁgaraṁgabhōgāla kiccina ma
<lb n="22" break="no"/>gama kramameṭlaṁnnanu [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>] pōṁ
<lb n="23" break="no"/>kapeṟukaṁ <unclear>gē</unclear>saripāṭi ka <unclear>1</unclear>
<lb n="24"/>pōṁkamōpuna vīsālu 2
<lb n="25"/>nuvvulabhaṁḍiṁ gēsaripā ka 1
<lb n="26"/>kolucubhaṁḍi vīsālu 2
<lb n="27"/>prattibo<unclear>ddu</unclear>naṁ gēsaripā ka 1
<lb n="28"/>kolucu<unclear>peṟu</unclear>ka vīsāmu 1
<lb n="29"/>Ākulamōpuna 50 Ākulu
<lb n="30"/>nūnepe<unclear>ṟuka</unclear> vīsālu 2 ta
<lb n="31" break="no"/>lamōpuna vīsāmu 1 cilla
<lb n="32" break="no"/>ra mōpuna vīsālu 2 gare
<lb n="33" break="no"/>ṁṭakolumā nūne gareṁ ṭeṁ
<lb n="34" break="no"/>ḍū<unclear>nnu</unclear> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> magamamīṁda mari<unclear>ṁ</unclear>
<lb n="35" break="no"/><unclear>nni</unclear> rāgabhōgālaku nasī<unclear>ma</unclear>
<lb n="36" break="no"/>nukēsari Aḍḍugu Ī kramāna
<lb n="37"/>nubhayanānādēśīni Ācaṁ
<lb n="38" break="no"/>drārkkamugā nistimi <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dī
<lb n="39" break="no"/>niki nevva raḍḍapaḍḍā
<lb n="40" break="no"/>nu samayadrōhulu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="41"/>A <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kkavulapeṭṭeṁ gēsaripā
<lb n="42" break="no"/>ṭi ka<note n="304-2">The inscription is left unfinished.</note>
</p>

